------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Built on the Accord Project
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project is built on, and interoperates with, the Accord Project's open
standard for computable contracts (https://accordproject.org), used under the
Apache License, Version 2.0:

  - Concerto modeling language and the `@accordproject/concerto-*` packages
    (concerto-core, concerto-codegen, concerto-cto, concerto-metamodel,
    concerto-util, concerto-vocabulary)
  - Cicero / TemplateMark contract templating

The Concerto data models (`*.cto`) and templates in this repository are the
authors' own work in the `org.openclaw.*` namespace; the JSON Schemas and
TypeScript types under `data/templates/` are mechanically generated from those
models by `concerto-codegen`. The Accord Project and its contributors are
gratefully acknowledged.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Recorded model outputs
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The evaluation cassettes under `data/eval/` contain recorded completions from
third-party commercial language models (OpenAI, Anthropic, DeepSeek), captured
for offline-reproducible research evaluation. They are published on the
understanding that each provider's terms permit research use and redistribution
of recorded outputs; see `data/eval/DATACARD.md`.
